STATE
v.
Charles Gene ROGERS. No. 165A84-5. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 5, 2005. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, C. Branson Vickory, III, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 3rd day of August 2005 by Defendant to Dismiss:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference this the 5th day of August 2005."
